reviewText: Saw the series and had to have it. Missed a lot from the broadcast and now have the missing links!

These two DVD's are a must have for any UFO enthusiast. Brand new still in the plastic wrap. I pretty much got these two DVD's for the price of one. Definitely a great buy, and I am looking forward to buying the 3rd season. Very interesting series about the UFO phenomenon. Awesome deal, would buy again!
